  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The privacy screens of the proposed roof terraces, because of their size and appearance would be an inappropriate development in this Conservation Area, failing to maintain and/or enhance the appearance and character of this Old Chiswick Conservation Area. The proposals therefore would be contrary to Local Plan policies CC1; CC2; CC4; SC7 and the Council's Residential Extension Guidelines (2017) and the intent of the National Planning Policy Framework.",
    "Reason : 2 - The privacy screens of the proposed roof terraces, because of their reduction in height would lead to overlooking and loss of privacy to the neighbouring properties. Thus, it is contrary to Local Plan policies SC7, CC1 and CC2 of Local Plan, policies of London Plan and the National Planning Policy Framework"
